title: Blazing 5 - Wild Card Weekend
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Wild Card Weekend
description:
Colin talks with RJ Bell of PreGame.com & FOX Sports Radio about his Blazin' 5 picks to find out which ones the sharps in Vegas agree or disagree with.

This week's games:


Colts @ Bills

Rams @ Seahawks

Washington @ Tampa Bay

Bears @ Saints

Browns @ Steelers


Plus, Colin gives out a bonus pick not in his Blazin' 5.
